    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, line a baking tray with <strong>baking paper</strong>, then slice the <strong>ciabatta<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> thin slices, and add to the tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 6 min</p><p>Combine the <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> </strong>the<strong> remaining crab meat </strong>in a bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy crab mix</strong></p>",
