      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>curried sweetcorn soup</strong> in bowls with the <strong>chilli crab crostinis</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish the <strong>chilli crab crostinis</strong> with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Top the soup with the <strong>reserved sweetcorn</strong> and the <strong>remaining chopped chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
